				<td colspan="2"><span>I did the Earring of the Solstice thing for FT1 and some nice int and sta on that earring.  For the archtype AA's so far I have CA1, CS1 and MC1.  Right now, at 58, the FT1 and MC1, adding an extra 2 mana per tick, seems to work quite well for me.  I do find myself running out of mana sometimes when swarm kiting but I can, with some extra chanting tossed in, swarm indefinitely.  
<br />

<br />
FT stacks with itself, so having multiple FT items has a cummulative effect.  Viscid Slime Gloves for example are FTIV, combined with the earring would be 5 mana per tick.. the cap on this is 15 mana per tick, combined with Mental Clarity 3 and the AA that adds 1 more to health and mana regen.. forget the name of it.. you could have up to 19 mana per tick regen.  Prior to FT and AA's we were just screwed, one nice new thing for the bards<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
